		<hr size="1">/ooc I agree 100% This is a TEAM PvP server NOT a LIGHT vs. DARK (though in the past I have made that mistake in thinking).<BR>/ic<BR>Well Bezzinal your words ring clear and true.<BR>It is hard for me to belive that you are from the same "race" of traitors that turned your back on the Royal House of Thex.<BR>I agree the lesser races should be destoyed.  <BR>The Humans are an interesting breed, able to learn many skills yet never being true masters. This is a slave stock, they just don't know it yet. <BR>The Short races should all BURN. They have no redeeming qualities what-so-ever.<BR>Now I come to your race, the Elves. <BR>Your time has come. True, you have had your moment of victory over us during the Crown Wars. That moment has now passed. I would say that I respected the elves for this, however in you ignorance you allowed your blood to become polluted. The result of this, are the so called Half-elves. <BR>I wish to remind you that a HALF elf is still HALF something else, most likly Human.<BR>This shows your weakness. <BR>The Teir'Dal would NEVER pollute our blood lines as your race seems eager to do. <BR>Our skin may have turned dark, our eyesight might have been altered, but at our core we are more Elven, more PURE than you or the rest of your kind could ever hope to be.<BR>Know this as truth.</P><P>Nallaael of The Lost Legion</P><P>"Genocide is one of the most tiring thing one can do...next to playing soccer."</P><P><BR><br>&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;<br></font>
